verbose_text: For SOD levels, the treatment groups showed a significant increase compared with that of the SHRSP-Veh group at 10 and 20 weeks (XREF_FIG, P < 0.05), while SOD levels were higher in the two amlodipine treatment groups compared with their respective counterparts (P < 0.05, SHRSP-Aml6 vs. SHRSP-Los6, and P < 0.05, SHRSP-Aml16 vs. SHRSP-Los16).
